Notes: PSU scores the game's final 10 points, after trailing 76-75 with 2:11 to go.
Kami Scrivner hits 6-6 FTs in the final 49 seconds to seal the win. Scrivner
and Amanda Davied combine for 29 second-half points.
Game.Officials: Phil Griffin (referee),  Jim Shockley,  Rick Glidewell
